aott/analysis/dataflow/live_variables.runa
Live Variable Analysis Module for AOTT Optimization

This module provides live variable analysis for the Runa AOTT system including:
- Backward dataflow analysis for liveness
- Use-def chain analysis
- Live range computation
- Register pressure calculation
- Dead store elimination
- Live variable interference graphs
- Spill cost estimation
- Loop live variable analysis
- Function boundary liveness
- Conditional liveness tracking
- Partial liveness analysis
- May-must liveness computation
- Live range splitting points
- Cross-block liveness propagation
- Liveness-based code motion
:End Note

Import "dev/debug/errors/core" as Errors

